  "subject": "Add pooling capability",
  "commit_message": "Add pooling capability\n\nAdd an optional feature that that supports session pooling, wherein\nmore than one host can be active at a time.\nSeparate publish() methods for each Message type.\nUse policy bus for communication with internal dmaap topic.\nAdd Message.checkValidity().\nSwitch to real timers.\nReformat per coding style guidelines.\nAdd hooks to extract request id after event decode.\nAdd FilterableTopicSource.\nRemove hooks to extract request id after event decode.  Change\nto provide an extraction method instead.\nAdd comments.\nAdd junit tests.\nAdd super() to default constructors.\nAdd BasicStateTester to facilitate testing of State classes.\nChange TypedProperty to SpecPropertyConfiguration.\nAdd general-purpose FeatureEnabledChecker class.\nRestructure properties using embedded properties, eliminating the need\nfor FeatureEnabledChecker.\n\nChange-Id: I521e68159455b5847863a4276455cce4480e8beb\nIssue-ID: POLICY-577\nSigned-off-by: Jim Hahn <jrh3@att.com>\n",
